The four United States Geological Survey (USGS) 1:24,000 scale topographic maps used to determine the boundary of The Burn of Columbia Valley viticultural area are titled: 

(1) Sundale NW, OR-WA, 2017; 

(2) Goodnoe Hills, WA, 2017; 

(3) Dot, WA, 2017; and 

(4) Sundale, WA-OR, 2017.
